# IO Chat - Google Gemini API key (for local `npm run dev`).
#
# 1. Get a key: https://aistudio.google.com  →  Get API key  →  Create
# 2. Copy this file to `.env.local`  (which is gitignored - NEVER commit a key)
# 3. Paste your key below in .env.local
# 4. Restart the dev server so Vite picks it up:  npm run dev
#
# On the deployed demo (no env key in the build) you can instead paste the
# key into the IO Chat page - it is stored only in your browser.

VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=
